{"talk":{"id":45837,"name":"Gangadhar Patil: How we're helping local reporters turn important stories into national news","description":"Local reporters are on the front lines of important stories, but their work often goes unnoticed by national and international news outlets. TED Fellow and journalist Gangadhar Patil is working to change that. In this quick talk, he shows how he's connecting grassroots reporters in India with major news outlets worldwide -- and helping elevate and expose stories that might never get covered otherwise.","slug":"gangadhar_patil_how_we_re_helping_local_reporters_turn_important_stories_into_national_news","recorded_at":"2019-04-15 00:00:00","published_at":"2019-10-08 19:51:20","updated_at":"2021-11-01 00:22:26","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":597,"name":"TED2019"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/afdc91206e180b4c1f029e4f97ee741d6acd4b01_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/afdc91206e180b4c1f029e4f97ee741d6acd4b01_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/afdc91206e180b4c1f029e4f97ee741d6acd4b01_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/afdc91206e180b4c1f029e4f97ee741d6acd4b01_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/9ca356e1d6f95b98026a2de39c9261614d0cc8f4_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GangadharPatil_2019U-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":2381421,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GangadharPatil_2019U-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":6535751,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GangadharPatil_2019U-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":11604303,"mime_type